<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM8.8.4">
<l>uḷainta variyum māṉiṭamu muṭaṉāyt tōṉṟa voṉṟuvittu</l>
<l>viḷainta cīṟṟam viṇvetumpa vēṟṟō ṉakalam veñcamattu</l>
<l>piḷantu vaḷainta vukirāṉaip peruntaṇ cenneṟ kulaitaṭintu</l>
<l>kaḷañcey puṟaviṉ kaṇṇapurat taṭiyēṉ kaṇṭu koṇṭēṉē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The one with curved claws when he appeared as a roaring lion</l>
<l rend="indent">and a man uniting together,</l>
<l>Splitting his opponent’s chest in heated battle,</l>
<l rend="indent">so the heavens withered from the fury which arose,</l>
<l>I, his servant, saw for myself in Kaṇṇapuram</l>
<l rend="indent">with land [that villagers] make</l>
<l>Into threshing fields, having hewn</l>
<l rend="indent">clusters of large, fresh red paddy.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
